3. Booking & Appointment Website

Example: Therapist, coach, consultant, barber

What it is

A service website with scheduling and availability.

Logic

Time slots

Booking confirmation

Availability rules

Email notifications

Design

Calm, trustworthy design

Simple forms

Clear CTAs

Why it’s good

Extremely common real-world use case

Plugins handle heavy logic

Easy to explain to employers/clients

2️⃣ Custom User Roles & Permissions

Different users see different things.

Roles:

Admin

Provider

Client

Logic:

Providers can:

Edit their profile

Manage availability

View bookings

Clients can:

Book sessions

View booking history